---
title: Chimichurri Pork Fillet & Lemony Greens with Garlic Roast Potatoes, Feta & Pine Nuts
description: Pork nights are the best nights and this dish is sure to wow anyone who tastes it. A succulent pork fillet is cooked in our
chimichurri seasoning and potatoes roasted with garlic. Serve it up with a side of lemon drizzled greens for a pork dinner that is luxurious in flavour and appearance.

